data.description: WOW! Come check out this wonderful 4 bed, 2/1 bath Cottage Grove home! Coming in at 2044 sqft with an amazing back yard that backs up to a peaceful wooded area and located on a dead end st. Owner had new trex deck, Back fence and a full alpha turf yard installed so you don't have to spend your time mowing! New carpet in 2022, Fresh painted kitchen, interior laundry room, gas fire place, & oversized garage with large attic space for storage. Come see the charm of this home for yourself!
